cols. This Treat All initiative prevents virus transmission at both the individual and community level. Henceforth, around 12 lakh PLHIV are availing the benefits of free treatment at approx. 530 ART centers.", "002-normal": "For the past few years, there is an increase in the number of PLHIV who requires proper treatment and thus there is an increase in the monitoring needs. Henceforth to monitor viral load suppression, NACO scales up the Viral Load Testing facility."}}